spawnHarrierGamePieces() - Method in class birdgame.Model
spawnHarrierGamePieces() will randomly generate a food, enemy, or special food of a random type for the player these obstacles will match those for a harrier, and include Bunnies, Mice, Foxes, and Raccoons.
spawnOspreyGamePieces() - Method in class birdgame.Model
spawnOspreyGamePieces() will randomly generate a food, enemy, or special food of a random type for the player these obstacles will match those for a osprey, and include Snakes, Fish, Eagles, and Planes.
